-----------------------
PLAY MINI
-----------------------
this sample app demonstrates how to expose existing (Scala) Akka services via HTTP using Play as a library
(Notice: there is nothing play specific about this project, no app, conf folder.)

for more information about using play as an HTTP library, please see https://github.com/typesafehub/play2-mini

------------------
HOW TO RUN THE APP 
------------------

this app requires the latest version of play (not available in a repo yet).

please see top level README for installation. Once that's done:

> sbt 

> run 

